item.title: Private server help
item.dc:creator: @fireman7778 fireman7778
item.description:
@fireman7778 wrote:

ok, first of all in lamens terms, you say you have a hamachi server, a hamachi server would mean you have a privet server, hamachi is only used to let other people connect to your privet server, seceondly most ppl dont start from scratch they use a source, i got my source from Mod taharoks server source builder i believe, anyway once you have a source that is when you start edting, but you will need jdk-6-ui or somthing like that and a compiler, i use mod taharoks perfect compiler version 1.9. those are the tools youll need to get started hope this helped a bit.
